/---------\
| WELCOME |
\---------/

This is SYNGUI, a GTK+-based GUI for the supernova spectrum synthesis code
SYN++.


/--------------\
| DEPENDENCIES |
\--------------/

    - GTK+ v2
        - I haven't tested this on GTK+ v3.

    - gtkmm >=2.24
        - These are the C++ bindings to GTK+ v2.

    - yaml-cpp v0.5.0
        - The yaml-cpp API changed significantly between v0.3.0 and v0.5.0, so
          you definitely need the newest version.

/----------------------\
| COMPILE INSTRUCTIONS |
\----------------------/

Run something like

    g++ run_syngui.cc `pkg-config --cflags --libs gtkmm-2.4 yaml-cpp`

I've tested this on Ubuntu 12.10 and Macports-based GTK+ on OS X 10.6.
